Just recently decided to get back in to mixing after I found out there's a magnetic mixer on the market that doesn't cost hundreds of dollars, and also had these flavors around that are now close to expiring soon from a similar recipe (sans CAP Cinnamon Danish Swirl..Just Cinnamon Danish from when I found it)..&#xD;
&#xD;
Mixed it up and tried a couple drops after a few hours...Already on point to the flavor I was expecting versus what I got originally when I tried the original 'shake, breathe, steep' method we've all been taught...&#xD;
&#xD;
Just have to try to get through 120ml of flavouring before they turn on me now...
